<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>📖 建立預設集教學</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Noto+Serif+TC:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', 'Noto Serif TC', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f6f3;
            color: #1e1e1e;
            padding: 0 24px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 30px 0 30px;
        }

        .back-link {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #b8865b;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 15px;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        .back-link:hover {
            color: #8a6b4a;
        }

        .back-link .arrow {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-right: 6px;
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }

        .back-link:hover .arrow {
            transform: translateX(-4px);
        }

        .page-title {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #1e1e1e;
        }

        .page-title span {
            color: #b8865b;
        }

        .page-sub {
            color: #8a8a8a;
            font-size: 17px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .step-card {
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 20px 24px 24px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
            box-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .step-card .step-num {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #b8865b;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 2px 14px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .step-card .step-content {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }

        .step-card .step-text {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 0;
        }

        .step-card .step-text h3 {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            color: #1e1e1e;
        }

        .step-card .step-text p {
            color: #6b6b6b;
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .step-card .screenshot {
            flex-shrink: 0;
            width: 200px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
            background: #ffffff;
        }

        .step-card .screenshot img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            display: block;
        }

        .step-card .screenshot .caption {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #b0b0b0;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 6px 8px;
            background: #faf8f6;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
            line-height: 1.3;
        }

        .btn-rect {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #1e1e1e;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 14px 48px;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            letter-spacing: 0.3px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .btn-rect:hover {
            background: #3a3a3a;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 10px;
            padding: 28px 0;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
            color: #b0b0b0;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #b8865b;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        @media (max-width: 700px) {
            .page-title {
                font-size: 28px;
            }
            .container {
                padding: 20px 0;
            }
            .btn-rect {
                padding: 12px 32px;
                font-size: 14px;
            }
            .step-card {
                padding: 16px 16px 20px;
            }
            .step-card .step-content {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }
            .step-card .screenshot {
                width: 100%;
                max-width: 300px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">

        <a href="autumn.html" class="back-link">
            <span class="arrow">←</span> 回到質感秋天
        </a>

        <h1 class="page-title">📖 建立 <span>預設集教學</span></h1>
        <p class="page-sub">將調色數據儲存為 Lightroom 預設集，一鍵套用到任何照片。</p>

        <!-- ===== 步驟 1 ===== -->
        <div class="step-card">
            <span class="step-num">步驟 1</span>
            <div class="step-content">
                <div class="step-text">
                    <h3>開啟 Lightroom 並進入「編輯」面板</h3>
                    <p>在 Lightroom 中打開一張照片，點擊右上方的「編輯」圖示。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="screenshot">
                    <img src="https://www.image2url.com/r2/default/images/1783952840755-7a1a6c52-89a5-43c0-93f5-75712c729b54.png" alt="Lightroom 編輯面板" />
                    <div class="caption">編輯面板位置</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- ===== 步驟 2 ===== -->
        <div class="step-card">
            <span class="step-num">步驟 2</span>
            <div class="step-content">
                <div class="step-text">
                    <h3>建立預設集</h3>
                    <p>在編輯面板中，找到並點擊「建立預設集」的選項。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="screenshot">
                    <img src="https://cdn.phototourl.com/member/2026-07-13-8597bbf5-ce78-48b4-9386-0000acdaea77.png" alt="建立預設集" />
                    <div class="caption">建立預設集位置</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- ===== 步驟 3 ===== -->
        <div class="step-card">
            <span class="step-num">步驟 3</span>
            <div class="step-content">
                <div class="step-text">
                    <h3>命名預設集</h3>
                    <p>在「命名預設集」視窗中，輸入您的預設集名稱（例如：質感秋天）。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="screenshot">
                    <img src="https://www.image2url.com/r2/default/images/1783953135772-7db72dd0-526b-4838-bd83-a0eec5b73342.png" alt="命名預設集" />
                    <div class="caption">輸入預設集名稱</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- ===== 步驟 4 ===== -->
        <div class="step-card">
            <span class="step-num">步驟 4</span>
            <div class="step-content">
                <div class="step-text">
                    <h3>儲存預設集</h3>
                    <p>確認名稱後，點擊「建立」或「儲存」，預設集就會儲存在「使用者預設集」中。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="screenshot">
                    <img src="https://www.image2url.com/r2/default/images/1783953899361-8192949b-df02-4d83-9ea8-8feca8def023.png" alt="儲存預設集" />
                    <div class="caption">儲存預設集</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- ===== 步驟 5 ===== -->
        <div class="step-card">
            <span class="step-num">步驟 5</span>
            <div class="step-content">
                <div class="step-text">
                    <h3>查看使用者預設集</h3>
                    <p>儲存後，可以在「預設集」面板的「使用者預設集」中找到剛剛建立的濾鏡。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="screenshot">
                    <img src="https://www.image2url.com/r2/default/images/1783954019263-f44559f4-be45-4a45-8619-25ee2bf2f9ba.png" alt="使用者預設集" />
                    <div class="caption">使用者預設集畫面</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- ===== 步驟 6 ===== -->
        <div class="step-card">
            <span class="step-num">步驟 6</span>
            <div class="step-content">
                <div class="step-text">
                    <h3>套用濾鏡</h3>
                    <p>點擊剛剛建立的預設集，就能一鍵套用質感秋天濾鏡到任何照片上！</p>
                </div>
                <div class="screenshot">
                    <img src="https://www.image2url.com/r2/default/images/1783954235719-07f68bd9-20ed-45a1-9acf-7138a411c3ba.png" alt="套用濾鏡" />
                    <div class="caption">點擊套用濾鏡</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- ===== 回到質感秋天 ===== -->
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 10px;">
            <a href="autumn.html" class="btn-rect">← 回到質感秋天</a>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>用色調記錄生活，讓每張照片都有故事。</p>
            <p style="margin-top:4px;">
                聯繫我：<a href="mailto:amuy930315@email.com">amuy930315@email.com</a>
            </p>
            <p style="margin-top:2px; font-size:12px; color:#d0d0d0;">
                © 2026 濾鏡教學
            </p>
        </div>

    </div>

</body>
</html>
